message: Wow. So stunning!! Kaila please DM me. 😊

I’ll lay out by my pool this weekend and see if I can catch up to your skin color!!

I will babe! 😎
Hey what’s a stunning woman like you doing texting strangers on the internet?
Trying to expand my horizont, idk honestly just open to making new connections that feel right
That’s cool. I hope I fit that category and someday maybe more 😉
I hard a tight beard for a year. Lol
u def look better with it
I like that
This pic is from Costa Rica
Really?
oh that sounds cool, hows Costa Rica?
Costa Rica was great. Beautiful country
are you from over there originally?
Torres sounds spanish
No I was born here in California but my parents were born in Italy
ah yeah, forgot u said that
sorry
It is a Spanish sounding name. Way back many Spanish people were in Italy
that makes sense

Yes. 2. My son is 17 and my daughter is 19

Let's text tomorrow. Good night

Like a baby! Lol

Now I’m at the driving range practicing golf. 😊
Okay thats cool, have fun, I'm also gonna go to Pilates now. Catch up later
K

Was good, now lunch. Hbu?
Just finished my workout
Now time for a snack

Cheese crackers grapes and apple
Enjoy

Just some rice with chicken. Standard indo food haha
Thank u Len 🙂
Would be nice if you could tell me a bit more about u and ur life

Sure. What would you like to know. 2 kids, divorced for 7 years. Did great in school. Have an Engineering degree and a Masters in Business. I’ve done well professionally. I’m a president of an aerospace company. I grew up playing all kinds of sports. I like now to play golf. I stay active and call and exercise daily. I love the sun and the beach. I like to travel and spend time taking care of my home and yard. That’s a start. lol
Thank you very much for that nice introduction. How old are I kids and how long were u married?
My kids are 17 and 19. I was married for 15 years
How about you? Siblings, school, work, live with parents????
I do have 3 younger siblings. currently studying accounting and I do live with my parents
Tell me a secret you never told anyone
Can’t think of one. Lol
haha come on
Hey there Kaila. Did you have lunch?
How’s your weekend?
Yes I had chicken with soft bones, you can also eat them. Weekend is good. Took my friends dog to the beach today. Hows ur weekend? Got you tan on the pool?
Yes Mr tan is looking good!! lol
More Sun today. I’m trying to catch up to you!!

I’ll change with you a bit later. 6:00 AM here 😊

Oh shoot that’s right! 🤣🤣🤣
Well I tried!
How was your exam? What are you studying?
Dinner was great! Pasta with homemade meat sauce, garlic bread and salad. 😊

It was accounting information systems, I study accounting. So you are a good cook ya? Haha thank you, thats very sweet of you. You dont have a new girl over there?
Yes a good cook. Lol. No new girl, just waiting for you babe!!! lol
Hahah come on, a successful handsome guy like u must have girls left and right

🤣🤣🤣. Well …. Fir the first few years after divorce, I just focused on my kids Now I’m starting to think about myself. I’m really busy though with work and taking care of my house and yard and having my kids every other week. Clean, ship, cook, exercise, etc

Yes. It’s the end of the month. But it’s a short week. We celebrate July 4th

Yes it is

Yeah. Probably bbq and swim
Ok now you’re getting ready to sleep !! 🤣🤣

Hopefully dressing up like the mafia boss

I’m going to make you part of the “family”. Hahaha
Hey! BTW, who takes all those pictures of you? I want that job!!! 😘

Not really lol but I would love to be your photographer !!!!!￼

Hope you’re having good day
Hey there my mafia boss
I am, just a bit busy with exams. How are u

Yes I do

One of these days it would be great to have a chance to video call with you. 🤔🤔. Maybe one day you will feel comfortable and have a moment to spend

Sweet dreams then soon for the sexy mafia boss
